<plot>A 1980s photographer and advertising designer trying on clothes in a vintage clothing store find themselves on a tour of 1930s nightclubs. They travel to Berlin, London, New York, New Orleans and Paris, taking part in the unique music and dance of each city. In each nightclub, George (Lewis Collins) finds the same woman--a woman he repeatedly falls in love with.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?014025</url></doc>
